               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I trusted all the customers on my own hands—I received this money—I meant to make it good—ray master accepted these terms, and the next day had me taken—his daughter owes me 13<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I let him take out beer on credit—if he took out a pot of beer, it was his duty to bring me the money—I have no reason to believe he trusted any<lb></lb>body on his own account—my daughter does not owe him 13<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., to my knowledge.</p>
